# konoplay.com launch

When the user asks about **launch**, **production**, **custom domain**, **konoplay.com**, **deploy**, **hosting**, or **moving off github.io**:

1. **Read `LAUNCH_KONOPLAY_COM.md`** at the repo root first — it has the full checklist, decisions, and current blockers.
2. Production domain is **`konoplay.com`** (not `.gg`, not github.io long-term).
3. Staging may stay on `https://kononiaka.github.io` (root) until cutover.
4. OAuth/Twitch/Firebase/Google API key referrers must all use the **exact** production callback:
   `https://konoplay.com/auth/twitch/callback`
5. Do not confuse Google **API key** HTTP referrers (browser login) with Firebase **Authorized domains** or Twitch redirect URIs — all three must be updated on domain change.
